text: Narvik is an Norwegian town and municipality located in Nordland county. It has a population of 18,756 inhabitants in 2017. The area covers 2,023.03 square kilometres. ==Related pages== *List of mayors in Norway that are elected until 2027 == Other websites == * Narvik Kommune official website Category:Cities in Norway Category:Towns in Norway Category:Municipalities of Nordland
